Name: TC_LOGOUT_001
Precondition:
-User has an active account
-User logged in
-Dashboard is opened
Objective: To verify that the user can logg out successfully
Test Script (Step-by-Step) - Expected Re:
The three-dot menu is opened successfully and the logout option should be 
visible
User should be logged out successfully and redirected to the page
User should not be able to access dashboard after logout
